# Per-developer devcontainer resource caps. Copy to .devcontainer/.env to apply.
# With no .env (or all lines left commented), the container runs UNCAPPED.
#
# memswap_limit is TOTAL memory+swap, not swap alone. To forbid swap entirely,
# set DEVCONTAINER_MEMORY_SWAP equal to DEVCONTAINER_MEMORY.
# DEVCONTAINER_MEMORY=4g
# DEVCONTAINER_MEMORY_SWAP=8g
#
# V8 heap can't be derived from mem_limit — keep it consistent by hand:
# DEVCONTAINER_NODE_OPTIONS=--max-old-space-size=4096
